### ============================================================
### STUDENT BOOKMARKS API - REST Client Testing
### ============================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api

### Login siswa dulu
# @name loginSiswa
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "siswa",
  "nisn": "0001234567",
  "school_origin": "SMA Negeri 1 Bogor",
  "unique_code": "BUDI0001234X9YZ"
}

###

### 1) GET BOOKMARKS (PAGINATED)
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/bookmarks?per_page=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSiswa.response.body.$.data.token}}

###

### 2) ADD BOOKMARK (ganti id sesuai job vacancy yang tersedia)
POST {{baseUrl}}/student/bookmarks/2
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSiswa.response.body.$.data.token}}

###

### 3) REMOVE BOOKMARK
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/student/bookmarks/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSiswa.response.body.$.data.token}}

###
